": ""}, {"cid": 2502760, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 477437, "reply_to": 2502294, "tag": null, "text": "大四报保不上研老狗，建议按照培养方案有多少报多少，卷高就行，不用多报。", "timestamp": 1631586763, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2503695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 477437, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同意，第一学期别忙得不可开交，结果啥也没学好", "timestamp": 1631595754, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2505320, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 477437, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "话说期中不是可以tkpl吗", "timestamp": 1631611115, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2505325, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 477437, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大一上（26学分）感觉还是很清闲的啊.....", "timestamp": 1631611147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2506686, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 477437, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感谢🙏dz提醒，我及时悬崖勒马", "timestamp": 1631622165, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 477437, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "趁着还能退课提醒一下大一的朋友们，请在第一学期酌情选课，不要图学分多，有趣的课以后还有机会选。第一学期选太多了绩点容易崩盘，不仅是后面要补漏洞，对心理上也是很大的压力和打击。我大一上只选了必修课24学分，先把绩点的基础稳住了，往后至少心里压力不会太大", "timestamp": 1631578446, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631622165, "url": "", "vote": {}}}